{"tid":738513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【劉慧卿召喚】敵本土賣港大中華 曾志豪 節目中講粗口被港台正式停職！","createTime":"2018-07-11T14:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T15:28:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"deca2e9bd56c8d637c98120b7859bb04cfb62075","tid":738513,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406464-20180711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406464-20180711.htm&d=AJHdO6HFtdvUc6xrauw8np4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a6fc29ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406464-20180711.htm&h=66accf26\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406464-20180711.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1406464_1_L_20180711193619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1406464_1_L_20180711193619.jpg&h=cbfa84bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港電台節目主持人曾志豪早上在節目中說粗口。港台機構傳訊及節目標準組總監伍曼儀表示，曾志豪早上在一個節目中，播放宣傳聲帶時「開錯咪」，說了「不適合說話」，由明日起暫停曾志豪主持電台節目，直至本月22日。<br />\n<br />\n伍曼儀說，港台已即時嚴正處理，並訓斥對方主持節目不專業，港台就事件致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/4b/MmZbg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F4b%2FMmZbg.gif&h=74cccdc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ee892b8b0af57f88f6b388b23e497f9736def3d","tid":738513,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sa81p-4EtYM/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fsa81p-4EtYM%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=e0a46202&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"506c23062b35b11c849c410ef36d0ec590c5b3cc","tid":738513,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1